WHO   — The Unmaker — the conscious cosmic force of entropy and destruction — the adversary that works through accident, water, and human jealousy to tear every made thing back down to nothing
WHAT  — the conscious cosmic force of entropy and destruction — the adversary that works through accident, water, and human jealousy to tear every made thing back down to nothing
